itle>劏房孽主真係畜生都不如</title><updated>2025-08-12T12:32:06+08:00</updated><author><name>共棍鳩毛黨</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-12T12:32:06+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573570362"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573570362"&gt;如題&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16427002" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573570362" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250812/20250812_686d0e19da2ef5a57c56uKschMOQz6ha.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a123b6/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250812/20250812_686d0e19da2ef5a57c56uKschMOQz6ha.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16427002_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16427002&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250812_121702_com.facebook.katana_edit_659575456146230.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (209.56 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-12 12:32&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32005275&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1058894467689ac489273ed7_53969533"/><published>2025-08-12T12:32:06+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a88030f927e2e6b8242e9cddf2dceea7</id><title>施政報告在即 地建會梁志堅：倡放寬100元印花稅至樓價上限600萬</title><updated>2025-08-12T12:32:51+08:00</updated><author><name>海邊笨拙的榴槤</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-12T12:32:51+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573570371"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573570371"&gt;原文網址: 施政報告在即地建會梁志堅：倡放寬100元印花稅至樓價上限600萬 | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60265751%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=68bafe3102ad7b8be6ceced6245fc133&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;如果成功落實，樓價肯定爆升&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32005276&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1058894467689ac489273ed7_53969533"/><published>2025-08-12T12:32:51+08:00</published></entry></feed>